post_text:
Update to the start of our summer workouts/Football camp in July.

Int/MS: 4-6 Youth Football Camp from July 7-9 is Canceled. I will be reaching out to all that have signed up, so that your camp fee is re-imbursed.

Tentative July Schedule: (Can change at any time due to COVID)
HS: Boys: July 1 & 2: 7:30-9:30 AM Strength/Speed/Equipment Hand-out. Girls 9:30-11:30 AM Strength/Speed
HS: July 6- 9: 7:30-9:30 AM Strength & Speed w/ Football Mini Camp occurring on July 7 & 9. Those days the boys will be done at 10:30 AM. Girls: 9:30-11:30 Strength/Speed
HS: July 13 - 16: 7:30-9:30 AM Strength & Speed w/ Football Mini Camp occurring on July 14 & 16. Boys will be done at 10:30 AM on those days. Girls: 9:30-11:30 Strength/Speed
HS: July 20-23 & 27-30: Camp 8-10:30 AM w/ weights afterwards. JH camp are on same days but 8-10 AM. Girls: 7:30-9:30 AM Strength/Speed

Reminder that the waiver must be signed & returned before your child can take part in any summer activities. https://t.co/oggkd6mO91

🏅 Congratulations to our first Parkland Health Mart Play it Forward Athlete of the Week, Jefferson R7 running back Andrew Graves. 🏈 Graves scored 4 TD's in the season opener and recorded a safety as well. https://www.mymoinfo.com/2018/08/28/jefferson-r-7s-andrew-graves-named-the-first-parkland-healthmart-pharmacy-play-it-forward-athlete-of-the-week/
